whowrotethat-ext-desc: Zop a̱tyulyuut ma̱ng nkhang khwifeang mi̱ nwuan ma̱ng di̱di̱ri̱k mami a̱yaati̱kut  Wikipidya. WikiA̱nyan wa nang cet hu.
whowrotethat-ext-desc-beta: Zop nkhang a̱tyulyuut Wikipidya. WikiA̱nyan wa nang cet hu. Si̱ huni hwa yet nok BETA hu, mat maí hwa ma̱nyin.
whowrotethat-ext-longdesc: A̱nyan Wa Lyuut A̱hwa? (A̱WLA̱) yet bwak brauza hwa, zang hwa tyaat nkhang a̱tyulyuut ma̱ di̱di̱ri̱k ma̱ a̱yaati̱kut Wikipidya. Ka̱ a si̱ keang kyangmami hu, kyangta̱m hu na si̱ mya̱ra̱m a̱mgba̱m kyangmami mbwak a̱tyulyuut a̱nyiung wu. Ka̱ a nyap tazwa kyangmami, kyangta̱m hu na si̱ nghywut ma̱ng a̱tyulyuut wu khwifeang wu, a mbeang a̱cyuang nkhang khwifeang na. Ma̱ a̱mgba̱m A̱WLA̱ nwuat á̱nienta̱m yak lyen a̱vwuoneet ma̱ng nkhang a̱zama jhyuk, di̱ mi̱n lung nkhang gbangbang khwifeang na kap di̱n kap bah.

whowrotethat-state-pending: $1 shyia̱ di̱ nyia̱ lodi. Si̱ huni maai kyiak a̱banjen.

whowrotethat-error-contact-link: Ka̱ jhya̱ ji ya a̱son, lyiat ma̱ng a̱nzi̱t.
whowrotethat-ready-general: Keang a li nwuat mi̱ nwuat hu mbwak a̱tyulyuut a̱nyiung wu. Nyap mat á̱ghyang nkhang.
whowrotethat-tour-welcome-description: Tyia̱ kyangta̱m hu di̱n ta̱m neet shan a̱ta̱m ji. Keang tazwa lyuut a mmya̱ra̱m nwuat mi̱ nwuat mbwak a̱tyulyuut a̱nyiung wu. Nyap a li a̱tyulyuut wu ma̱ng a̱cyuang nkhang khwifeang na.
